| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1284 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 57ecd6df-30a5-57a2-93ab-b4e82d5b7097"
